#

Mexican Chicken Rice Bowl

40 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

Comfort FoodQuick MealOne Bowl

Description

A vibrant and satisfying bowl filled with seasoned chicken, colorful veggies, and fluffy rice, topped with fresh avocado and a hint of lime.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 1 pound
  • long-grain white rice: 1 cup
  • black beans: 1 can
  • corn kernels: 1 cup
  • red bell pepper: 1, diced
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • lime: 1, juiced
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • chili powder: 1 teaspoon
